    <string name="onboarding_welcome_title">Welcome to Snake</string>
    <string name="onboarding_welcome_body">Guide the snake to the glowing food and grow with every bite. It never stops moving - steer it clear of walls, obstacles and its own tail, and chain quick bites into a combo multiplier for serious scores.</string>
    <string name="onboarding_welcome_controls_hint">Steer your way - swipe anywhere, tap to turn, or use a classic D-pad. Change it any time in Settings.</string>
    <string name="onboarding_controls_swipe">Swipe</string>
    <string name="onboarding_controls_tap">Tap to turn</string>
    <string name="onboarding_controls_dpad">D-pad</string>
    <string name="onboarding_food_title">Eat to grow</string>
    <string name="onboarding_food_body">Food appears one piece at a time. Most of it feeds the snake, but read the colour - some pieces are working against you. Ignore a piece too long and it vanishes, so be decisive.</string>
    <string name="onboarding_food_grow">Grow</string>
    <string name="onboarding_food_grow_desc">Green pieces add length and score. The larger the piece, the bigger the reward.</string>
    <string name="onboarding_food_shrink">Shrink</string>
    <string name="onboarding_food_shrink_desc">Warm pieces trim your tail - handy when you are boxed in, but they cost points.</string>
    <string name="onboarding_food_mystery">Mystery</string>
    <string name="onboarding_food_mystery_desc">A \"?\" hides a random grow or shrink. Eat it to find out which.</string>
    <string name="onboarding_specials_title">Power-ups &amp; hazards</string>
    <string name="onboarding_specials_body">Deeper into a run, rare special blocks appear. Power-ups help you; hazards are ringed in red and make life harder. Prefer a gentler game? Turn hazards off any time in Settings.</string>
    <string name="onboarding_powerups">Power-ups</string>
    <string name="onboarding_hazards">Hazards</string>
    <string name="onboarding_jackpot">Jackpot</string>
    <string name="onboarding_explosion">Explosion</string>
    <string name="onboarding_lightning_desc">Speeds the snake up for a short, frantic burst.</string>
    <string name="onboarding_star_desc">Invincible: pass straight through walls, obstacles and your own tail.</string>
    <string name="onboarding_freeze_desc">Slows time right down so you can pick a safe line.</string>
    <string name="onboarding_jackpot_desc">A large score bonus plus a few extra segments at once.</string>
    <string name="onboarding_quake_desc">Shakes the whole board, making it hard to read for a while.</string>
    <string name="onboarding_explosion_desc">Splits the snake in two; the severed tail stays lethal until it fades.</string>
    <string name="onboarding_snail_desc">Slows you to a crawl - manageable, but you lose your rhythm.</string>
    <string name="onboarding_modes_title">Four ways to play</string>
    <string name="onboarding_modes_body">From white-knuckle sprints to pure flow. Every mode keeps its own records for each difficulty and board size.</string>
    <string name="onboarding_mode_endless_desc">The pace ratchets up the longer you survive. One life, no ceiling - how far can you go?</string>
    <string name="onboarding_mode_time_attack_desc">Two minutes on the clock, score multipliers for the brave and a double-points Fever finale.</string>
    <string name="onboarding_mode_campaign_desc">Fifteen hand-shaped boards with three lives and checkpoints - and every lap spins faster.</string>
    <string name="onboarding_mode_zen_desc">No walls, no hazards, no hurry: the edges wrap around. Only your own tail can end the flow.</string>
    <string name="onboarding_meta_title">New reasons to play, every day</string>
    <string name="onboarding_meta_body">Short runs are never wasted - everything you do feeds your progress.</string>
    <string name="onboarding_meta_daily">Daily Challenge</string>
    <string name="onboarding_meta_daily_desc">One seeded run per day, the same for every player. Beat it daily to build your streak.</string>
    <string name="onboarding_meta_missions">Today\'s Missions</string>
    <string name="onboarding_meta_missions_desc">Three rotating goals refresh each day - clear them in any mode you like.</string>
    <string name="onboarding_meta_achievements">Achievements &amp; records</string>
    <string name="onboarding_meta_achievements_desc">Over 30 feats to unlock, plus a best score for every mode, difficulty and board.</string>
    <string name="onboarding_meta_skins">Skins &amp; arenas</string>
    <string name="onboarding_meta_skins_desc">Earn snake skins and animated board worlds, then dress the whole game in them.</string>
    <string name="onboarding_replay_hint">You can reopen this guide any time from Settings.</string>

